data.text:
Davit Aghajanyan , is an Armenian actor and model. He is known for his role as Tigran on Full House.

Davit Aghajanyan was born on March 5, 1992, in Yerevan, Yerevan, Armenia. His birth geographical coordinates are 40° 10’ 52” North latitude and 44° 30’ 49” East longitude. Davit Aghajanyan is currently 32 years old.

Astrologically, Davit Aghajanyan falls under the Sun sign of Pisces, with Cancer as his Ascendant, Pisces as his Moon sign, and Aquarius as his Black Moon Lilith sign.
